    public class LevelX
extends Level
    The LevelX class is an eXtendend version of Level class. It introduces thow new levels, the DEBUG, which is designed to identify debug messages and the FATAL, which identifies heavily error messages
    Further the LevelX class provides two masks for existing Levels: ERROR which equals Level.SEVERE and WARN which stands for Level.WARNING.
    Thus the new ordering of the levels is (in descending order):
    • FATAL (highest value)
    • ERROR
    • WARN
    • INFO
    • CONFIG
    • DEBUG
    The native Level class provides levels below DEBUG.
